{"tid":1792772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"匯豐最驚美國制裁，全民恐慌性拋售/short匯豐股票","createTime":"2019-12-22T01:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T15:30:57.000Z","uid":48234,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"16f3bd8467acb9aa3a3e0f6de28bf911bf66862a","tid":1792772,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T01:58:17.000Z","msg":"制裁損失最大，拋售/落short係其次<br />\n如果有內鬼搵到辦法偷運走匯豐金庫啲黃金仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d734b5c2b83a84040b8891e4f42ec366938c1e99","tid":1792772,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:01:13.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3CHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=2e73ce3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"e001bf18a1cdf6f97be69df47f9a8569df21cd1f","tid":1792772,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:01:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"504b83bee13b98b93f2ad132d74128331a903bae","tid":1792772,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:29:56.000Z","msg":"全球一齊經濟制裁，本身就係一種「超級大裝修」<br />\n如果再加埋全球匯豐內鬼都走去偷走黃金，匯豐倒閉指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e701cb334326cf944acb6caa5b0fcc8f6ff0a8","tid":1792772,"uid":69334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"想睇滙豐死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86e219167d604a8d33549642656853a25e56c2e","tid":1792772,"uid":219767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d734b5c2b83a84040b8891e4f42ec366938c1e99","tid":1792772,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:01:13.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3CHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=2e73ce3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:34:14.000Z","msg":"唔好幫推呢d on9低智post"},{"pid":"f87b87010b180bf5a42236e4ccad4e3844c6d411","tid":1792772,"uid":266207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:03:05.000Z","msg":"我求吓大家繼續支持匯豐啦，俾次機會好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n建議大家千祈唔好用以下方法令匯豐除咗賺少咗錢之外仲要倒蝕<br />\n<br />\n戶口除咗要keep少少結餘之外，仲要經常有轉帳呀<br />\n<br />\n因為低結餘帳戶，匯豐冇錢賺之外每個account仲可能要蝕埋maintenance fee俾個客。而每單transaction佢哋個system係要成本嘅。最貴係櫃位 &gt; 專人電話理財 &gt; 語音電話理財 = ATM &gt; 網上理財(係咁上下）。以我幾年前嘅印象係每單交易，佢哋成本係十幾至$50蚊一單（希望有知情人事update 吓有冇改變）<br />\n<br />\n如果大家一日不斷係saving 轉錢去支票戶口，又係支票戶口轉返轉頭會點呢？<br />\n<br />\n之前政府都講咗每宗交稅嘅交易涉及政府開支平均為$3蚊，如果大家經匯豐$1蚊1蚊咁交稅比政府會點呢？<br />\n<br />\n大家千祈唔好咁做呀，我求吓你哋"},{"pid":"0c11bccb25d0fc1f660716a865cb032331435032","tid":1792772,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:16:00.000Z","msg":"已重倉熊左匯豐"},{"pid":"cb21dd8b135229c88602ad8ba5227f79b055cdc6","tid":1792772,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf68aa7106e3f8cc00931a75f8c2a6f5081d930","tid":1792772,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"大家星期日有時間，記住加入香港金融業職